description: Do not run GPU-dependent scripts from the agent
alwaysApply: true
---

# No GPU Execution by Agent

- Do not execute training/evaluation scripts that require GPUs.
- Do not launch long GPU jobs directly from the agent.
- Prefer preparing commands, editing configs/scripts, and using `DRY_RUN=1` when available.
- If runtime verification is needed, ask the user to run the command on a GPU-capable node.
